txt.en: You have encountered the threatening Ephalzôr. This high commanding Black Númenórean sorcerer patrols The Wastes for intruders.
Ephalzôr can be found patrolling The Wastes.\n\nYou have encountered Ephalzôr and should defeat this foe for those who brave these harsh lands.
